creator: FBCT College
descriptionHtml:
This app is designed to help you stay connected to the First Baptist Tuscaloosa Student Ministry and be informed on all the exciting things we have planned! With this app, you can
- Stay up to date on upcoming events
- Tune into The TTOWN Students Podcast
- Listen to past messages
- View ministry photos
- Stay in contact with your life groups and D-Groups
- Fill out applications and forms for teams and events
And much more!!
descriptionShort: Welcome to the one-stop-shop for all things TTOWN Students!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Added support for Android 12
- If enabled, Subsplash Messaging notifications now displays the sender’s avatar on Android 11+
- Misc. bug fixes and improvements
